Class DistributionCentre

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.DistributionCentre
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class DistributionCentre
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    a distribution center locates in a city and has products and its quantity in this center. Its information includes:
    • city it locates
    • a map between product and its quantity in this center
